      "content": "wait r u sure? i read somewhere that blood thinners and ibuprofen might not mix well. i dont want to do anything too risky, but this headache is really intense and i just want some relief. if the ibuprofen works locally like you said, does that mean it wont affect how my warfarin works? i just need to know if i can take 400mg now.",
